Ok. so the weekend was okay. i heard somewhat exciting news. not gonna elaborate. but here's the weekend.

Friday - blew. i went to oxford lake. bored as hell. went to BAM afterwards. saw nathan. only decent person there. it was ...nice.

Saturday - Went to Books-A-Million and stayed the whole night. from like 7:30 - 11:30. but it was nice. i saw great people. saw lame people too. soo, the crowd started to fade as normal, and i called matt. he said he had tried get in touch with me all night. oops =X so he came up to books a million and hung out about an hour. went back to nikis. sleepy time.

Today - Came home. Called Matt. Matt met the rents'. they seemed to get along. niceee. went to his place. came home. here i am.

someone better call. or else. grr.

Man oh man i'm super sickly. i think. see i didnt sleep much last night at all. i woke up with my eyes completely Dialated. they are HUGE. i cant eat. period. the sound of food sounds repulsive. i'm shaking super bad. ekk. i just dont know whats wrong with me! i wanna get over this...soon!

xox
Amy
<3

Not quite sure of the plans for the 4th. Anyone want to hang out? let me know. Not FOR sure if i will be here. Depends on Lisa. But i might be in GA. Depends. Matt wants me to go to his show. so Maybe... i Dont know. i want to. but it depends. i probably will. But if not..yeah.

Ok...so i need to rephrase myself. I dont think that Fri/Sat were the best nights of my life...

PERHAPS, last night. indeed

Relationships...?

hickeys are the devil

XoX
Amy
<3

|no one| to have. |no| hand to hold.
i suppress my position as a means to silence the truth.
tormented by my every undying devotion to |you|

Oh man. I'm so pissy. Well not really. Just disappointed. 7 angel 7 plagues was here 6/12 not 7/12. i wasnt thinking, and i was like oh well they are coming JULY 12....damn. 6 = June. sux for me. either way. i missed probably one of the greatest shows i would have ever seen. m a n, i dunno whats wrong with Jared. He has been acting awfully odd lately. even Matt agreed with me. oh well. maybe just pms. i hope. i dont like him like this. Me and matt are supposed to hang out this week. But, well, he does work. Plus with their show this friday((the 4th)), they have to practice all week. he called me after practice last night. around...11? i felt so bad for him. he sounded so tired. Hopefully tonight...yah. hopefully tonight. xox Amy <3
Thur. June 26 @ 7PM and $7 CAVE9/BIRMINGHAM The Black Dahlia Murder The Red Chord, Premonitions of War, Deadwater Drowning, Dearest Fae, Solo Mono, Of Means And Ends Anyone care to Join?

I am in one of those moods, where you just know you are going to die soon. i was walking down my hallway, and i think, i'm going to die soon. My body is freaking out on me. I feel weird. I feel like i am in a dream. One that i have been in before. several times. I get in these weird moods. People irritate me more that they should. i miss more people(than i should). everything is pretty. music has lots more meaning. WHAT THE HELL xox Amy <3 is my problem?
